818
00:38:44,840 --> 00:38:46,940
(We'll put on the dress right away tomorrow.)

819
00:38:47,410 --> 00:38:48,740
(Our outfits...)

820
00:38:49,210 --> 00:38:52,210
(Their outfits call for a photo wall.)

821
00:38:52,550 --> 00:38:53,749
(No matter what, )

822
00:38:53,750 --> 00:38:55,819
(let's do a photo session in the living room.)

823
00:38:55,820 --> 00:38:56,979
Even if we failed to win the meal coupon...

824
00:38:56,980 --> 00:38:59,620
(The siblings have prepared dresses as you can see.)

825
00:39:00,550 --> 00:39:02,420
You look like you're at an award ceremony.

826
00:39:03,420 --> 00:39:05,829
I'll be so upset if we can't eat out after doing this.

827
00:39:05,830 --> 00:39:08,660
We're at an award ceremony like the Baeksang Awards.

828
00:39:09,430 --> 00:39:11,600
(As the siblings asked for a photo wall...)

829
00:39:16,170 --> 00:39:17,170
(Meal-coupon Awards)

830
00:39:17,171 --> 00:39:19,170
(Dining Awards)

831
00:39:20,840 --> 00:39:24,410
(The ceremony begins now.)

832
00:39:26,010 --> 00:39:28,220
