842
00:40:04,120 --> 00:40:05,850
Gosh. This is hilarious.

843
00:40:06,020 --> 00:40:08,660
- We'll take a photo.
- Photo? Let's take photos.

844
00:40:10,960 --> 00:40:11,960
(As an a-list star from Korea makes an appearance, )

845
00:40:11,961 --> 00:40:12,990
Are we good?

846
00:40:13,390 --> 00:40:14,899
(the press is heated.)

847
00:40:14,900 --> 00:40:15,959
Here are the hearts.

848
00:40:15,960 --> 00:40:17,559
